</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>香港 Samsung 手機免費借機試玩，體驗日期 + 機種詳情</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/19/galaxytrial/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=galaxytrial</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 19 May 2022 10:45:07 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1100717</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Samsung 三星香港今日宣佈首次推出智能裝置體驗活動「Galaxy 免費體驗計劃」，用家可先免費試用 Sa [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Samsung 三星香港今日宣佈首次推出智能裝置體驗活動「Galaxy 免費體驗計劃」，用家可先免費試用 Samsung 旗下多款旗艦手機、平板電腦，在試用一段時間之後才決定是否購買。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Z-Fold3-5G.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1100719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Z-Fold3-5G-694x518.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="518" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Z-Fold3-5G-694x518.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Z-Fold3-5G-768x574.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Z-Fold3-5G.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Samsung 指知道好多用家買機時會心大心細，而「Galaxy 免費體驗計劃」就讓用家使用過裝置，覺得所帶來的新功能、使用體驗感到滿意才確定購買，讓用戶更易找到他們心儀的智能裝置。</p><p>「Galaxy 免費體驗計劃」將於 2022 年 5 月 20 日至 6 月 30 日期間推出，用戶可在活動期間借用列表所示裝置中的其中一部，試用期為 5 天，歸還裝置後才決定是否購買。今次計劃所涵蓋的裝置包括：</p><p>Galaxy Z Fold3 5G 智能手機</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zfold3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1100723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zfold3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zfold3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zfold3-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zfold3.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>Galaxy Z Flip3 5G 智能手機</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zflip3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1100724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zflip3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zflip3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zflip3-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zflip3.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>Galaxy S22 Ultra 5G 智能手機</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-S22-Ultra.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1100718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-S22-Ultra-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-S22-Ultra-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-S22-Ultra-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-S22-Ultra.jpg 964w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Galaxy Tab S8 Ultra 平板電腦</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Tab-S8-Ultra.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1100720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Tab-S8-Ultra-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Tab-S8-Ultra-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Tab-S8-Ultra-768x513.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Galaxy-Tab-S8-Ultra.jpg 965w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>用戶可到官方網站報名，並選擇借用裝置，填寫有關個人資料，同時選擇還機日期、時間。用戶可選擇前往中環或尖沙咀的三星專門店取機。用戶在借機時需要繳付指定金額的按金。體驗完畢歸還借用的裝置後，用戶可選擇購買新機。三星專門店會為用戶轉移資料到新機上，而透過此計劃出機的用戶，可獲贈無線閃充雙充電板 P5400（建議零售價 HK$698）。</p><p>資料來源：Samsung</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
